{"tid":1562206,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際大學排名機構罕有提醒不明政治前景 或致大學國際人才流失及排名下降","createTime":"2019-09-12T02:27:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T02:33:40.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"33149516beb3bdd8145d11701b110d37345c16a3","tid":1562206,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:27:20.000Z","msg":"《逃犯條例》修訂爭議持續，有非本地學者及學生因此而放棄來港大學任職、就學或交流，有大學排名機構亦罕有提醒本港大學在面對政治前景不確定，有機會面臨國際人才流失。<span style=\"color: red;\">有專家指如情況持續，有機會產生雪球效應，影響收生、外地學者來港任教意慾，甚至令大學排名下降</span>。<br />\n<br />\n英國泰晤士高等教育最新公布的2020年世界大學排名，本港4間大學排名均下跌，排名機構指所用數據早於香港發生社會運動前，故並未反映其影響，<span style=\"color: red;\">但指本港大學在面對不確定的政治前景及中港關係，會令大學在投資及國際人才流動面臨風險</span>。<br />\n<br />\n城市大學回應承認，香港社會近日的紛爭對香港的大學帶來影響，尤其有些非本地的學者及學生取消來港任職、就學或交流；理大則指，今年學生交流計劃的參與，以及取錄非本地生的情況均與以往差別不大，未見有受社會情況影響。<br />\n<br />\n學友社學生輔導顧問吳寶城表示，外地知名學者選擇前往任教的大學時，地區安全及包容程度均會列作考慮因素，相信會有學者認為香港相對不安全，且本港政治環境將來會否惡化仍是問號，學者或會因而卻步，人才有機會流向鄰近與香港背景相似、但政治穩定的新加坡。若情況持續，他預料會影響外地人來港升學或任教的意慾，令大學排名下跌，從而再影響大學獲得的資源，令排名再進一步下跌，產生雪球效應。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2449649/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2449649%2F&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FWLTbr5529Gqcy%2B2MeRGono%3D&h=99a23498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2449649/</a>"},{"pid":"11146324359bf917e3c146806134dd868336fb87","tid":1562206,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:27:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"1cb9184e5f23f70742603f3b77fd9807628cfe70","tid":1562206,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5fa5271667581450a3549ea9e4169715b6942a","tid":1562206,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:30:14.000Z","msg":"淋病又考第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"149aceb75df498b38bd16dbd3b99b146e7b7caac","tid":1562206,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:33:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"584e2a2c1f7358388297a1fc5f282683ceb4129d","tid":1562206,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:33:36.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB/TG搵我地香港自由之書阿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n國難五金專訪 [開鋪事直請留意國難五金FB]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/137